These are Puzzles for 3x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-1::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: hiking, traveling, skydiving, sudoku, domino-climbing, board-games, chess
7 different games are played: monopoly, go, whist, poker, billiard, domino, backgammon
There are 7 different favourite beverages: tea, water, 7up, mirinda, iced-tea, cola, juice
 1. the person who's hobby is domino-climbing is on the far left##1
 2. the person drinking water is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 3. the person drinking juice is between the person playing go and the person playing monopoly##2
 4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 5. the person playing go is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 6. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person drinking juice##1
 7. the person playing poker is between the person drinking mirinda and the person who's hobby is domino-climbing##2
 8. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 9. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
10. the person who's hobby is chess is the person playing whist##1
11. the person playing domino is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
12. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
13. the person drinking tea is the person playing billiard##1
14. the person who's hobby is board-games is between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking juice##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |    7     |
| Hobby   | domino-climbing | hiking     | board-games | traveling | sudoku | chess  | skydiving  |
| Game   | monopoly  | poker        | go  | backgammon     | domino   | whist       | billiard   |
| Beverage         | water   | juice | mirinda    | 7up  | iced-tea | cola | tea |

