.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-2::.
7 different games are played: billiard, backgammon, canasta, domino, chess, bridge, monopoly
The people have 7 different hobbies: fishing, traveling, ebonyd-games, cooking, singing, dancing, sudoku
