 2. the person who's hobby is singing is the person who's hobby is singing##1
 3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 4. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
 5. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person playing monopoly##1
 6. the person playing billiard is the person who likes grey##1
 7. the person playing billiard is between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the person who likes lavender##2
 8. the person who's hobby is ebonyd-games is on the left of the person playing chess##1
 9. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
10. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
11. the person playing chess is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
12. the person who likes mauve is the person playing backgammon##1
13. the person playing domino is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
14. the person playing domino is on the right of the person who likes ivory##1
15. the person playing backgammon is on the far right##1
16. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3       |    4     |   5    |     6     |    7     |
