12. the owner of the fish is the person who likes pink##1
13. the person who likes lavender is on the far right##1
14. the person who's sport is snowboarding is between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the person who's sport is basketball##2
15. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1

