11. the person who likes emerald is the doctor##1
12. the person driving the train is on the far left##1
13. the carcher is the person driving the subway##1
14. the person who likes ebony is on the far right##1
15. the person driving the skateboard is on the far right##1
16. the person driving the snowmobile is between the writer and the person who likes emerald##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4     |     5      |     6      |  7   |
